@startuml state Diagram

!theme plain
skinparam BackgroundColor #fafafa
skinparam RoundCorner 20
skinparam state {
  BorderColor #16342c
  BackgroundColor #edfdf8
  ArrowColor #24768b
}

title Home Library Management System — Book State Diagram

[*] --> Available : Book added to user's collection\nand possibly to global list of books

Available : Owner holds the book
Available : Can be found in global search

Available --> Reserved : Friend requests reservation\n[friend connection verified]

Reserved : Date for reservation and return recorded
Reserved : Inbox notification sent to owner

note right of Reserved
  Triggers InboxMessage
  of type LendingRequest to owner
end note

Reserved --> Lent : Owner confirms lending\nand the user borrows on the lending date
Reserved --> Available : Reservation cancelled\n[by borrower or owner]
Reserved --> Available : Reservation expired\n[no confirmation]

Lent : Book is with borrower
Lent : Return date set as previously

Lent --> ReturnPending : Borrower initiates return
Lent --> Overdue : Return date exceeded\n[reminder sent to inbox]

ReturnPending : Owner must confirm the return

note right of ReturnPending
  Triggers InboxMessage
  of type ReturnRequest to owner
end note

ReturnPending --> Available : Owner confirms return

Overdue : Return reminder notification sent\nboth to borrower and to owner
Overdue : Book still with borrower

note right of Overdue
  Triggers InboxMessage
  of type ReturnReminder
  to borrower and owner
end note

Overdue --> ReturnPending : Borrower initiates return

Available --> [*] : Book removed from collection\nStays in the global list of books

@enduml
